@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<main>
    <section class="row" aria-labelledby="aspnetTitle">
        <h1 id="title">Simple Blog Site</h1>
        <p class="lead">Asocial media plateform where you can share your ideas and communicate with friends.</p>
        <p><a href="https://asp.net" class="btn btn-primary btn-md">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </section>

    <div class="row">
        <section class="col-md-4" aria-labelledby="gettingStartedTitle">
            <h2 id="gettingStartedTitle">Posting features</h2>
            <p>
                Here you can create new post, update any existing post and also you can delete your posts. You can see other users post if the post privacy is public, or you can see friends post where priavcy can be friends or public. But you can not see posts where post privacy is only me or friend if he/she is not your friend.
            </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301865">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </section>
        <section class="col-md-4" aria-labelledby="librariesTitle">
            <h2 id="librariesTitle">Like and Comment</h2>
            <p>You can like and can do comments on other users(or own) post and also you can able to edit or delete your comments from posts.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301866">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </section>
        <section class="col-md-4" aria-labelledby="hostingTitle">
            <h2 id="hostingTitle">Chating</h2>
            <p>You can easily chat with any user from chat option. Also you can able to delete messages that you sent. </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301867">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </section>
    </div>
</main>